Special Topics Ed-ventures
Join us for some of our Special Topics Ed-ventures. These programs will have distinguished guest speakers guiding the program. This is a great opportunity to learn in detail about different aspects of Biscayne National Park. Topics may include:  People of Biscayne, Black Caesar and other pirates of South Florida, Photography workshops, Lighthouses of Biscayne and many others. Look on our calendar for upcoming topics and dates.
